div.p:
Let every one here preſent before the


Lord, Pray to Him to be kept and preſerved by Him from this & all other great Tranſgreſſions. Keep back thy ſervant from preſumptuous ſins, let them not have dominion over me: So ſhall I be innocent from the great Tranſgreſſion. It is an excellent and needful part in our Litany;

                  From Envy, Hatred and Malice, and all Ʋncharitableneſs (& ſo from Murder one frequent curſed Effect of them;) Good Lord deliver us.
